{"kind":"article","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"}],"roleHeading":"Article","title":"How to Add a Permanent License","role":"article"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToAddAPermanentLicense","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService"],"anchor":"Related-Documentation"},{"title":"How-to Guides","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPreviewAndTest"],"generated":true,"anchor":"How-to-Guides"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Many apps offer two ways to buy: a recurring pro subscription and a one-time lifetime purchase. RevenueCat models both as entitlements; ","type":"text"},{"code":"RevenueCatPaywallService","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" checks each independently and surfaces them as the two flags on ","type":"text"},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"isPro","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" — active subscription.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"hasPermanentLicense"},{"type":"text","text":" — active lifetime entitlement."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The paywall plugin’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isGateSatisfied"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isPro || hasPermanentLicense"},{"type":"text","text":", so feature code keeps a single check while UI can branch on the underlying flags when it needs to."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For the entitlement-mapping rules and edge cases, see "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"text":"Before you start","anchor":"Before-you-start","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This guide assumes:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You have completed ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You have configured ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"two","type":"text"}]},{"text":" entitlements in the RevenueCat dashboard — typically ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pro"},{"text":" for the subscription and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lifetime"},{"text":" for the one-time purchase. The identifiers are arbitrary; only the strings need to match what you pass into the service.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Step 1: Pass the second identifier","anchor":"Step-1-Pass-the-second-identifier","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Replace the single-entitlement init with the two-arg form:"}]},{"code":["import SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","","let service = RevenueCatPaywallService(","    entitlementID: \"pro\",","    permanentLicenseEntitlementID: \"lifetime\"",")"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Both entitlements are now checked on every "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customerInfo()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customerInfoStream()"},{"type":"text","text":" yield, and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"restorePurchases()"},{"type":"text","text":" call. The active state of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"pro"},{"type":"text","text":" flows into "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"EntitlementSnapshot.isPro"},{"type":"text","text":"; the active state of "},{"code":"lifetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flows into ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"hasPermanentLicense"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The two flags are independent. A user with both active gets both flags set; a user with only one active gets only that flag set.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Step 2: Wire the service into the plugin","level":2,"anchor":"Step-2-Wire-the-service-into-the-plugin"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as the single-entitlement case — the plugin doesn’t need to know about the second identifier:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["plugins.register(","    PaywallPlugin<AppState, AppAction>(","        state: \\.paywall,","        action: AppAction.paywall,","        extractAction: { if case .paywall(let a) = $0 { return a }; return nil },","        service: RevenueCatPaywallService(","            entitlementID: \"pro\",","            permanentLicenseEntitlementID: \"lifetime\"","        )","    )",")"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","text":"Step 3: Decide whether feature code needs to branch","level":2,"anchor":"Step-3-Decide-whether-feature-code-needs-to-branch"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For most gated features, keep using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"store.paywall.isGateSatisfied"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["if store.paywall.isGateSatisfied { … }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This stays correct whether the user has a subscription or a lifetime license, and works identically in apps that don’t sell a lifetime SKU.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Step 4: Branch in UI when copy must differ","level":2,"anchor":"Step-4-Branch-in-UI-when-copy-must-differ"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the paywall sheet should be hidden for lifetime customers (so they’re not pestered to subscribe), or if the customer-center entry should be relabeled, branch on the underlying flag:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["if store.paywall.hasPermanentLicense {","    Text(\"Lifetime member — thank you!\")","} else if store.paywall.isPro {","    Button(\"Manage Subscription\") {","        store.send(.paywall(.presentCustomerCenter))","    }","} else {","    Button(\"Upgrade\") {","        store.send(.paywall(.request(reason: \"upgrade-prompt\")))","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Lifetime users typically have nothing to manage in App Store \/ Settings. Hiding the customer-center button for them avoids dead-end taps."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"When to skip the second identifier","level":2,"anchor":"When-to-skip-the-second-identifier"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pass "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (or omit the parameter) if your app has no lifetime SKU:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["RevenueCatPaywallService(entitlementID: \"pro\")"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"hasPermanentLicense"},{"type":"text","text":" then stays "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":" regardless of any entitlements RevenueCat reports — even if the dashboard accidentally has a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lifetime"},{"type":"text","text":" entitlement that the service is not configured to check. See the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Lifetime entitlement is ignored when no permanent-license ID is configured"}]},{"type":"text","text":" test case for the precise behavior."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sell a lifetime entitlement alongside a subscription and surface both flags through the paywall plugin."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtoaddapermanentlicense"]}],"references":{"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToImplementService":{"kind":"article","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToImplementService","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtoimplementservice","title":"How to Implement the Service","abstract":[{"text":"Wire ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" into the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwiduxPaywall"},{"type":"text","text":" plugin so the store sees real-time entitlement updates from RevenueCat."}],"role":"article"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/ServiceReference":{"url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/servicereference","title":"Service Reference","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/ServiceReference","kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"API reference for ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"RevenueCatPaywallService"},{"text":" — the RevenueCat-backed ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"text":" conformer that the paywall plugin consumes.","type":"text"}],"role":"article"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/EntitlementMapping":{"kind":"article","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/EntitlementMapping","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/entitlementmapping","title":"Entitlement Mapping","abstract":[{"text":"How RevenueCat’s ","type":"text"},{"code":"CustomerInfo.entitlements","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" translates to Swidux’s "},{"code":"EntitlementSnapshot","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"role":"article"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/HowToPresentTheUI":{"abstract":[{"text":"Attach the ","type":"text"},{"code":"revenueCatPaywall","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"revenueCatCustomerCenter","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" view modifiers from ","type":"text"},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywallUI","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to a root view, driven by ","type":"text"},{"code":"PaywallState","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"title":"How to Present the UI","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall\/howtopresenttheui","kind":"article","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/HowToPresentTheUI","type":"topic"},"doc://SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall/documentation/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall\/documentation\/SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","url":"\/documentation\/swiduxrevenuecatpaywall","title":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall","abstract":[{"text":"RevenueCat adapter for Swidux’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallPlugin"},{"type":"text","text":". Implements "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PaywallService"},{"type":"text","text":" against "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Purchases.shared"},{"type":"text","text":", ships a controllable mock for previews and tests, and pairs with "},{"code":"SwiduxRevenueCatPaywall